snippet.title: SolChicks Alpha Version Trailer | Gamefi | Best NFT | Solana | Leading Play-to-Earn RPG Game
snippet.description:
SolChicks Saga is an NFT based Play-to-Earn game, and we encourage the trading and exchanging of SolChicks NFTs so that players will experience the breadth and depth that SolChicks Saga offers.

This trailer marks the beginning of the era of the SolChicks Saga. While this version is complete, there will be a lot of bug-testing and general testing to improve the game as the developers work hard to get the second Alpha version ready for the holders of the genesis NFTs to play.

Make sure you’re armed with a SolChicks NFT before the game launch 
https://linktr.ee/solchicksmint

Follow us on our socials to keep up with daily game updates
https://linktr.ee/solchicksnfts
